804
00:39:25,917 --> 00:39:27,583
What is this?

805
00:39:27,583 --> 00:39:28,583
They want
to go home.

806
00:39:28,583 --> 00:39:30,917
No, they're staying.

807
00:39:30,917 --> 00:39:32,542
(<i> communicator beeps</i> )
Number One.

808
00:39:32,542 --> 00:39:34,250
RIKER:
We're in position.

809
00:39:34,250 --> 00:39:35,959
Hold for orders.

810
00:39:35,959 --> 00:39:37,667
BEVERLY:
The radiation
levels on Aldea

