812
00:39:40,709 --> 00:39:42,000
It is similar to what
was experienced

813
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:44,625
on Earth
in the 21st century

814
00:39:44,625 --> 00:39:46,417
when the ozone layer
deteriorated

815
00:39:46,417 --> 00:39:48,083
and surface
of the planet
was flooded

816
00:39:48,083 --> 00:39:49,792
with ultraviolet
radiation.

817
00:39:49,792 --> 00:39:52,000
The shield that protected
your world in one way

818
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,709
is weakening it in another.

819
00:39:53,709 --> 00:39:55,333
It is the radiation
of your own sun

820
00:39:55,333 --> 00:39:56,750
that is destroying you.

821
00:39:56,750 --> 00:39:58,875
You are trying
to confuse the issue.

822
00:39:58,875 --> 00:40:01,333
Please listen.

823
00:40:01,333 --> 00:40:03,875
You're all suffering
from radiation poisoning.

824
00:40:03,875 --> 00:40:06,291
Sterility is only
the latest symptom.

825
00:40:06,291 --> 00:40:09,125
If the children remain,
they will be affected as well.

826
00:40:09,125 --> 00:40:11,750
That's impossible.
Our scientists would have known.

827
00:40:11,750 --> 00:40:13,208
How could they?

828
00:40:13,208 --> 00:40:15,417
Your scientists have forgotten
how everything works.

829
00:40:15,417 --> 00:40:18,166
No, all lies.

830
00:40:18,166 --> 00:40:20,375
No, wait.

831
00:40:20,375 --> 00:40:22,625
Don't send them
back yet.

832
00:40:22,625 --> 00:40:25,208
What<i> if</i> they're right?

833
00:40:25,208 --> 00:40:27,208
Instead of
the children
being our hope

834
00:40:27,208 --> 00:40:30,208
what if we're
condemning them
to our fate?

835
00:40:30,208 --> 00:40:33,417
Rashella, they're just
protecting their own interests.

836
00:40:33,417 --> 00:40:35,542
As are we.

837
00:40:35,542 --> 00:40:37,250
But hear them out.

838
00:40:37,250 --> 00:40:38,917
The Captain and
Dr. Crusher are saying

839
00:40:38,917 --> 00:40:40,750
that the very thing
which has given us

840
00:40:40,750 --> 00:40:41,917
this wonderful world

841
00:40:41,917 --> 00:40:44,250
is what has caused
this tragedy.

842
00:40:44,250 --> 00:40:46,083
That's it, exactly.

843
00:40:46,083 --> 00:40:48,291
Your Custodian has controlled
you so completely

844
00:40:48,291 --> 00:40:50,458
