to question it.

845
00:40:50,458 --> 00:40:52,917
Lies, and the discussion
is over.

846
00:40:52,917 --> 00:40:54,125
(<i> faltering beeps</i> )

847
00:40:58,917 --> 00:41:00,458
(<i> communicator beeps)</i>
Commander Riker.

848
00:41:00,458 --> 00:41:01,792
