853
00:41:08,792 --> 00:41:09,834
Good.

854
00:41:09,834 --> 00:41:11,542
<i>Enterprise,</i>
this is Picard.

855
00:41:11,542 --> 00:41:13,041
Beam the children up.

856
00:41:13,041 --> 00:41:14,458
Wait.

857
00:41:14,458 --> 00:41:15,959
PICARD:
<i>Enterprise,</i> hold.

858
00:41:19,667 --> 00:41:21,792
Thank you.

859
00:41:21,792 --> 00:41:22,959
Let me get
the dolphin

860
00:41:22,959 --> 00:41:24,709
for you to take
with you.

861
00:41:24,709 --> 00:41:27,458
No, you keep it.

862
00:41:27,458 --> 00:41:29,125
I'll make
another one.

863
00:41:38,667 --> 00:41:39,709
All right, Harry?

864
00:41:39,709 --> 00:41:41,750
Yes, Captain.

865
00:41:41,750 --> 00:41:43,834
Okay, kids,
let's go home.

866
00:41:49,333 --> 00:41:51,083
PICARD:
Beam them up.

867
