869
00:42:05,583 --> 00:42:07,959
We're not here
to destroy you, Radue.

870
00:42:07,959 --> 00:42:09,417
We're going to help you.

871
00:42:27,625 --> 00:42:30,083
What is it?

872
00:42:30,083 --> 00:42:32,458
PICARD:
The legacy
of your progenitors, Radue.

873
00:42:32,458 --> 00:42:34,125
The source
of your power

874
00:42:34,125 --> 00:42:35,458
and your problems.

875
00:42:35,458 --> 00:42:36,583
DATA:
It is reading

876
00:42:36,583 --> 00:42:38,125
incredible amounts
of energy, sir.

877
00:42:38,125 --> 00:42:40,834
Even more since we've
taken down the shield.

878
00:42:40,834 --> 00:42:42,667
What are we going
to do with it?

879
00:42:42,667 --> 00:42:45,917
Learn all over again.

880
00:42:45,917 --> 00:42:48,959
All this time we've been
destroying ourselves.

881
00:42:48,959 --> 00:42:52,834
So sure of our
technological
invulnerability.

882
00:42:52,834 --> 00:42:56,083
Now we must learn to use
this power, safely.

883
00:42:56,083 --> 00:42:57,750
Will you let us
help you?

884
00:42:57,750 --> 00:42:59,625
Yes, please.

885
00:43:07,458 --> 00:43:09,000
Dad, I want
to be an artist

886
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:11,333
