to take calculus.

889
00:43:19,166 --> 00:43:20,959
Okay. Thanks, Dad.

890
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:26,417
It worked well, sir.

891
00:43:26,417 --> 00:43:29,125
We have successfully
re-seeded the ozone layer

892
00:43:29,125 --> 00:43:31,417
but for their atmosphere
to maintain its integrity

893
00:43:31,417 --> 00:43:33,333
they can never
use the shield.

894
00:43:33,333 --> 00:43:34,917
Or be cloaked again.

895
00:43:37,041 --> 00:43:38,041
You finished?

896
00:43:38,041 --> 00:43:39,542
Yes, Captain.

897
00:43:39,542 --> 00:43:41,375
And they're responding
very well to the treatment.

898
00:43:43,417 --> 00:43:45,291
The legend will die

899
00:43:45,291 --> 00:43:47,542
but the people
will live.

900
00:43:47,542 --> 00:43:49,834
